<li><i><a href="/wiki/We%27ve_Had_a_Hundred_Years_of_Psychotherapy_-_And_the_World%27s_Getting_Worse" title="We've Had a Hundred Years of Psychotherapy - And the World's Getting Worse">We've Had a Hundred Years of Psychotherapy - And the World's Getting Worse</a></i> (with <a href="/wiki/Michael_Ventura" title="Michael Ventura">Michael Ventura</a>) (1993)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Thought_of_the_Heart_and_the_Soul_of_the_World&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The Thought of the Heart and the Soul of the World (page does not exist)">The Thought of the Heart and the Soul of the World</a></i> (1992)</li>
