<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Anima:_An_Anatomy_of_a_Personified_Notion&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Anima: An Anatomy of a Personified Notion (page does not exist)">Anima: An Anatomy of a Personified Notion</a></i> (1985)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Inter_Views&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Inter Views (page does not exist)">Inter Views</a></i> (with Laura Pozzo) (1983)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Myth_of_Analysis:_Three_Essays_in_Archetypal_Psychology&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The Myth of Analysis: Three Essays in Archetypal Psychology (page does not exist)">The Myth of Analysis: Three Essays in Archetypal Psychology</a></i> (1983a)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Dream_and_the_Underworld&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The Dream and the Underworld (page does not exist)">The Dream and the Underworld</a></i> (1979)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Re-Visioning_Psychology&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Re-Visioning Psychology (page does not exist)">Re-Visioning Psychology</a></i> (1975)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Loose_Ends:_Primary_Papers_in_Archetypal_Psychology&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Loose Ends: Primary Papers in Archetypal Psychology (page does not exist)">Loose Ends: Primary Papers in Archetypal Psychology</a></i> (1975a)</li>
